      "content": "i mean... it's more than just being invisible though. it's the weight of it all. like why bother trying to stay connected or keep up appearances when it literally changes nothing? if i just gave up and let it happen, it feels like it would finally be quiet. no more trying to be seen. does that sound crazy?",
